<paragraph id="8BAFC711FFFC647A47D628D5FD87FA41" blockId="3.[151,1436,1445,2035]" box="[151,529,1445,1472]" pageId="3" pageNumber="33">
<emphasis id="B9641B03FFFC647A47D628D5FF75FA3E" bold="true" box="[151,227,1445,1471]" pageId="3" pageNumber="33">Color.</emphasis>
Black or brownish black.
</paragraph>
